						<summary>

						<p>On a pillar built into the wall of the temple of Gōpīnātha.</p>						

						<p>Dated Śaka 1449, <hi rend="italic">Sarvajit, Mārgaśira</hi> śu. 15, Saturday, corresponding to A.D. 1527, December 7.</p>						

						<p>Damaged. Records a gift of land to god Gōpīnātha-Perumāḷ by Pōti-nēḍu, son of Timmānāyuḍu and grandson of Chōḍa Pōti-nāyuḍu for the <hi rend="italic">daśamī</hi> festival.</p>						

						</summary>
